<h1>Multi-channel chat sessions on one Twilio-compatible API.</h1>
<p class="lede">VoiceTel Conversations gives application teams a single REST surface for SMS, MMS, WhatsApp, and in-app chat — same participant, same thread, same history — without re-implementing channel-specific glue for every project.</p>
