<section class="section-block">
	<h2>What Conversations gives you</h2>
	<ul class="features-grid">
		<li class="feature">
			<span class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">{% icon "chat-square-text" %}</span>
			<h3>Threaded multi-channel chat</h3>
			<p>One conversation resource collects every message a participant sends — SMS, MMS, WhatsApp, or in-app — so application state stays consistent regardless of which channel a user replies on.</p>
		</li>
		<li class="feature">
